{"tid":1472612,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"忍唔住都係想講，再咁落去呢個運動一撚定收皮","createTime":"2019-08-14T15:26:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T08:17:22.000Z","uid":124101,"like":64,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"864432df2b028a3cd25dcca95e3813df8638794c","tid":1472612,"uid":124101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:26:58.000Z","msg":"去到呢個位，成個運動終於去到一個真正既<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">樽頸位</span></span></strong>，可能大家覺得呢個會好似我地咁多次遇到既爭坳一樣會就咁過去，但係其實一早已經出現呢個情況：有啲人話前線唔聽勸，前線就話果啲人冷氣軍師。但實際上可能果啲被人話冷氣軍師既都係前線，只不過有住唔同既唸法。<br />\n<br />\n琴日係機場眼見好多人夾硬block遊客，好無奈。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">出左聲，被人話係鬼、唔好阻住、兄弟爬山。但係如果眼見一啲嘢造成既傷害遠大於成果，真係唔聽下人地既意見？</span></span></strong>我知道情緒主導左個運動，而且示威者都唔係完美，總會做錯事，但當有人好意提醒既時候，真係下下都用兄弟爬山去無視啲意見？真係下下都被某一派既兄弟完全主導個運動？<br />\n<br />\n就好似踢波咁，有人防守有人進攻，咁係人都知各司其職架啦，就好似我地個運動係兄弟爬山各自努力咁。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係各司其職唔代表防守既唔可以評論進攻球員，亦都唔代表可以冇戰術憑感覺踢。</span></span></strong>如果真係11人冇戰術各自發揮冇配合既話，呢對波一定會好屎波。依家香港呢隊波就係咁，可能我地呢種各自發揮既方式踢下地區聯賽仲可以，但一旦升班去一啲更強既聯賽，應付一啲更加複雜既活動果陣就會暴露弱點。而且我地冇大台，代表住一隊波係冇教練。一隊波可以冇教練，但冇教練唔代表可以冇戰術，我地要自己傾戰術，自己協調。而且，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一隊好既team絕對唔可以有一兩個人控曬波狂射，其他人就跟著折返跑。</span></span></strong>我地個運動有啲似係咁，雖然可能有啲部分既人會係陪襯會係做幕後嘢，但都唔可以係某一派既人完全主導呢個運動。<br />\n<br />\n講翻日頭係機場遇到既嘢，感覺好無力。立場講掉核彈都唔割但係唔代表支持丟核彈。但不如咁講，如果果粒核彈係對住中南海，冇人會指責你。但如果果粒核彈係對住平民區，咁好明顯個打擊就唔準確，動搖唔到敵人既根本，亦都會濫殺好多無辜，恐怕真係唔會個個都認同。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化其實代表住一種死攬，因為我地冇得再放棄任何一個兄弟，但咁唔代表討論同提醒係可以用兄弟爬山來掩蓋。</span></strong></span>因為如果有人做左啲嘢可能傷害到個運動而佢自己冇發覺既，我地有責任去提佢。<br />\n<br />\n同時，我唔係淨係話一啲唔肯聽意見既勇武，好多和理非都唔想理解勇武點解要咁做。就好似我所講不分化唔係一個口號，代表住我地必須要死攬係一起，因為我地冇得再喪失任何力量。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好多和理非好強潔癖，但其實dirty work都唔使你做，人地幫你做，試下唔好指責佢地？當然，如果dirty work冇對準方向，你係有必要出聲制止、提醒、不停提醒，但就絕對唔係割席。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n呢個又牽涉到另一個問題：好多人覺得自己只要表達一啲唔同既唸法，就會被人話係鬼，被人鬧，所以就選擇自我審查唔出聲。<strong><ins>我係度懇請大家，唔好指責同路人表達既任何一個言之有物既意見，因為咁樣真係會製造一個噤聲既情況出現。</ins></strong>同時我跪求咁多位有意見既人，係現場講，我知道一定會被人鬧，因為好多時群情洶湧，好難說服到人，但<strong><ins>唔好放棄，因為如果你驚被人鬧而唔出聲，好可能會放棄左一個拯救個運動既機會。被人鬧好難受，但呢個何嘗又唔係一個dirty work？就算大家唔敢做最前線，勸交呢啲dirty work唔係都唔敢啊？</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n香港人，共勉之。"},{"pid":"adb95b9ee29140f3f42bd5c3aae136b8ea408806","tid":1472612,"uid":124101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:27:29.000Z","msg":"自推10"},{"pid":"4eba0e063c32c6d81ad52dc0e6c62766cff645d5","tid":1472612,"uid":124101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:28:31.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"64278929995aa1ff815929d8c8ab654d524fe574","tid":1472612,"uid":124101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:29:02.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"0b12ce937819daacb85915f42847e21565a4f57a","tid":1472612,"uid":124101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:29:50.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"229ca1c304f5385c91783ccf7a43a5f5da03066b","tid":1472612,"uid":245371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:30:16.000Z","msg":"[思想改革] 抗爭者的思路<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aejQsNU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aejQsNU</a>"},{"pid":"51aaf32e5ebca7977cd3470846e0dacd3882cd00","tid":1472612,"uid":124101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:30:24.000Z","msg":"求下大家睇完佢"},{"pid":"6f72bf4519019f3de041299b5cd52d56477f46aa","tid":1472612,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:30:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg&h=42f5c084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png&h=4a3dc024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg&h=42d70b2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"02e9c8dca835532b7526fb56d974876808dde826","tid":1472612,"uid":124101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:31:32.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n5"},{"pid":"dafbe2b8627e54d1ff63361f7b0f814bc2212ab1","tid":1472612,"uid":124101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:32:23.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"4b99aca624f6c380d8c26eea3b0c6d540d3a1370","tid":1472612,"uid":201492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:32:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d988ce8a319e931ca6aa400e92583c919d56e41","tid":1472612,"uid":124101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:32:58.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"8c15347928764d2552f79e913846a57d1860c289","tid":1472612,"uid":34681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:33:34.000Z","msg":"正評"},{"pid":"3656ecd3f232878939efcaf624288b98bb146360","tid":1472612,"uid":115041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:34:55.000Z","msg":"不分不割！不過樓主可以正面少少😂"},{"pid":"454d49001a4e2fd4fbde0e7d37cb34cc63e97666","tid":1472612,"uid":174569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:35:28.000Z","msg":"818"},{"pid":"b67f71d6cd7bee2a2afbc5df48e51376334e0366","tid":1472612,"uid":124101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:37:30.000Z","msg":"之前仲有好多post講呢樣嘢，包括訂立行動守則等等，其實會比起我講既嘢更清晰具體。我只係想幫下大家理解下依家個運動面對既困境。但我所講到另一樣嘢就係潔癖，都影響緊呢個運動，需要大家正視。<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家係點，經過琴日我既每一個group都辯論緊運動既發展，獲益良多之餘亦有好多憂慮。"},{"pid":"0494728214b16cd964b6f3ec2c4b65989ee501bf","tid":1472612,"uid":124101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3656ecd3f232878939efcaf624288b98bb146360","tid":1472612,"uid":115041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:34:55.000Z","msg":"不分不割！不過樓主可以正面少少😂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:39:44.000Z","msg":"我會繼續做自己覺得冇錯既嘢，不賣不分不割之餘，亦都唔會因為驚被人屌而唔出聲唔勸交（唔係話叫人唔好撚黑警果啲）"},{"pid":"cdd3f4204beeb1d3fb6c607c00209793ce6105c5","tid":1472612,"uid":124101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:39:54.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"1283d190b65e2df0c57ff8c487663e0d4d19f4c3","tid":1472612,"uid":135475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:40:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nOBHFPP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnOBHFPP.jpg&h=8c063e7d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9f75ed2e42394568c40ab01b6e0daaa7342a5ff","tid":1472612,"uid":182933,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:40:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a17f2d79045aac6d38914bce7cbe65585470266b","tid":1472612,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:42:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c2432141bb1136724de0009ec3304164e9ed91a3","tid":1472612,"uid":258328,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:43:22.000Z","msg":"要學識藍絲式盲撐，合理化咗個行動先，再提出更好方案"},{"pid":"f45812ab892f911c295a244d66bfbbd9200d91d3","tid":1472612,"uid":268692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:44:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b350799823fc6246baf13af24b13c5320772f84a","tid":1472612,"uid":124101,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c2432141bb1136724de0009ec3304164e9ed91a3","tid":1472612,"uid":258328,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:43:22.000Z","msg":"要學識藍絲式盲撐，合理化咗個行動先，再提出更好方案"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:44:59.000Z","msg":"所以我都贊成係要死攬左先，因為我地既力量已經夠細唔可以再少..."},{"pid":"d6edd043b8612fbbdd11b3449426578a310e25b3","tid":1472612,"uid":124101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9f75ed2e42394568c40ab01b6e0daaa7342a5ff","tid":1472612,"uid":182933,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:40:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:45:57.000Z","msg":"sorry lo<br />\n有咩事大家唔怕講啫"}]}